```
main = evaluate (f [1..4000000] (0 :: Int))

f []     c = c
f (x:xs) c = f xs (c + 1)

```

```
main = do
    evaluate (f [1..4000000] (0 :: Int, 1 :: Int))

f []     c = c
f (x:xs) c = f xs (tick x c)

tick x (c0, c1) | even x    = (c0, c1 + 1)
                | otherwise = (c0 + 1, c1)

```

```
f []     !c = c
f (x:xs) !c = f xs (tick x c)

```

```
tick x ~(c0, c1) | even x    = (c0, c1 + 1)
                 | otherwise = (c0 + 1, c1)

```

```
tick x (!c0, !c1) | even x    = (c0, c1 + 1)
                  | otherwise = (c0 + 1, c1)

```

```
f []     c = c
f (x:xs) c@(!_,!_) = f xs (tick x c)

```
